***************************************************************************************

********** SWAGGER PROJECT  **********
https://app.swaggerhub.com/apis/jbpadilha/Rates/1.0.0

********** REQUIREMENTS  **********

1 -  JAVA 11
2 - DOCKER (IDEALLY)


********** BUILD THE APPLICATION  **********

1 - ./mvnw install
2 - docker build -t "rateprice" . // TO BUILD DOCKER IMAGE

********** RUN THE APPLICATION  **********

1 - ./mvnw spring-boot:run

ALTERNATIVE TO RUN THROUGH DOCKER:

1 - docker run -p 8080:8080 "rateprice"


********** ENDPOINTS AVAILABLE  **********

"/rates"
-> GET => Returns all rates available in a json file (rates.json)
-> PUT => Overwrite Json file with rates passed by parameter.
* If the json file is null, it returns an error

Sample:
{
    "rates": [
        {
            "days": "mon,tues,thurs",
            "times": "0900-2100",
            "tz": "America/Chicago",
            "price": 1500
        }
    ]
}


"/price"
* Requires 2 parameters (start => Zoned Date Time / end => Zoned Date Time)
-> GET => Returns the price available

Return sample:
{
    "price": 5000
}


********** TESTING THE APPLICATION  **********

1 - The tests will run during the initialization

ALTERNATIVE:

1 - To run the test just type:  "./mvnw test"